name: BreatheExcerise
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: breathing exercise
des: Controlled breathing is yoga practice which increases oxygen level in your brain reduces the stress, This skill will help you to practice famous 4 7 8 breathing exercise which is breathe in for 4 count and hold breath for 7 count and breathe out slowly for 8 counts, If you have difficult in practicing this exercise , try our simple breathing practice on "Breathe Therapy" skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
